1
00:00:05,340 --> 00:00:07,150
(Survival or Fall in Love)

2
00:00:07,150 --> 00:00:08,560
Survival is important,

3
00:00:08,560 --> 00:00:09,470
but I think

4
00:00:09,470 --> 00:00:11,000
sincerity matters more.

5
00:00:11,460 --> 00:00:13,000
Whether I stay or leave
doesn't matter.

6
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,960
I just wanna find someone I truly like.

7
00:00:16,120 --> 00:00:18,710
Do you think staying is more important,

8
00:00:18,710 --> 00:00:20,600
or finding someone you like?

9
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:23,280
If I don't find someone I like,

10
00:00:23,280 --> 00:00:24,390
staying is more important.

11
00:00:25,310 --> 00:00:27,600
Actually,
my goal when coming to the island

12
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:29,920
is to survive first, then fall in love.

13
00:00:30,690 --> 00:00:32,080
Are you scared of being eliminated?

14
00:00:32,080 --> 00:00:32,950
Yeah.

15
00:00:32,950 --> 00:00:33,520
Scared.

16
00:00:34,110 --> 00:00:34,590
If I'm out,

17
00:00:34,590 --> 00:00:35,560
I'll just start crying.

18
00:00:35,560 --> 00:00:38,310
So if you win, who will you choose?

19
00:00:38,720 --> 00:00:39,950
(Survive)
Want an invite?

20
00:00:39,950 --> 00:00:40,880
Sure.

21
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:42,240
Alright.

22
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:43,720
Zhang Zizheng, hurry!

23
00:00:43,940 --> 00:00:44,740
(Fall in Love)

24
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:45,940
What I'm thinking is

25
00:00:45,940 --> 00:00:46,430
(Fall in Love)

26
00:00:46,430 --> 00:00:47,300
one more vote.

27
00:00:47,300 --> 00:00:48,080
(Survival, Fall in Love)

28
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:49,080
Why not?

29
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:50,720
Did you enjoy the date?

30
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:51,310
Yeah.

31
00:00:51,950 --> 00:00:53,790
After he came back from the date,

32
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:55,840
the moment our eyes met,

33
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:56,880
I knew he'd changed.

34
00:00:58,080 --> 00:00:58,880
I'm doomed.

35
00:00:59,900 --> 00:01:01,590
At that moment,
I still thought about survival.

36
00:01:02,110 --> 00:01:03,910
I didn't get any new votes,

37
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:06,480
and I even lost the votes I had.

38
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:09,190
Right then, I felt

39
00:01:09,190 --> 00:01:10,480
I was too greedy.

40
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:12,230
Sometimes people are greedy.

41
00:01:12,230 --> 00:01:13,000
Greed, anger, and obsession.

42
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:13,870
None of them are good.

43
00:01:14,270 --> 00:01:16,480
It feels like you think you can

44
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:19,230
control many things, but

45
00:01:19,230 --> 00:01:20,680
you can't pull it off.

46
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:25,800
(Survival, Fall in Love)
I also really want someone to like.

47
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:26,910
(Survival)

48
00:01:26,910 --> 00:01:30,270
There's no one
I feel like getting to know deeply.

49
00:01:30,270 --> 00:01:33,270
All I can say is
I'm trying my best to survive.

50
00:01:33,740 --> 00:01:37,860
=Episode 5 (Part 1)=
=Survival or Fall in Love=

51
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,200
(Xuan/Liu, Yang/Ding,
DAY4 After Off-Island Date)

52
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,040
He's heartbroken.

53
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:40,830
You know.

54
00:01:40,830 --> 00:01:41,590
The person he likes

55
00:01:41,590 --> 00:01:43,510
is out on a date with someone else.

56
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,760
What's going on here?

57
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:48,830
Come chat.

58
00:01:48,830 --> 00:01:49,950
Come join us.

59
00:01:50,550 --> 00:01:51,310
A meeting.

60
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,080
Islanders.

61
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,510
Today's dates aren't final.

62
00:01:57,230 --> 00:01:59,120
Fate can still be rewritten.

63
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,680
All female islanders
staying on the island

64
00:02:02,270 --> 00:02:04,230
can compete again.

65
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,680
The winning girl

66
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:08,000
will get a Date Relay Card.

67
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:08,800
Relay.

68
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:09,830
Relay date.

69
00:02:09,830 --> 00:02:10,240
Relay.

70
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,900
(Date Relay Card)

71
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,910
No idea what the game is,

72
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:15,160
but Yang's

73
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,910
athletic skills are top-notch.

74
00:02:16,910 --> 00:02:17,720
So I think she

75
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:18,910
might just win it.

76
00:02:19,190 --> 00:02:20,470
A little excited,

77
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:22,520
and a little nervous.

78
00:02:24,910 --> 00:02:25,670
Let's go.

79
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:28,270
Have you ever risked it all for someone?

80
00:02:29,190 --> 00:02:30,520
When I heard

81
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,750
there's a new game,

82
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:33,720
my first thought was still to win.

83
00:02:34,110 --> 00:02:36,270
In any competition, you'd want to win.

84
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:38,240
I just want a chance

85
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,160
to chat more.

86
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,910
What does this mean?

87
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:46,630
Fan it into that basket.

88
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:48,550
What?

89
00:02:48,670 --> 00:02:49,830
This is so silly.

90
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,000
And it's a piglet.

91
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:54,000
Win it, make it my mascot.

92
00:02:54,260 --> 00:02:54,800
Lose…

93
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,880
If I lose, it gets stomped.

94
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,320
Lose,

95
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,270
and it's done for.

96
00:02:58,270 --> 00:02:59,160
"Kill" the piglet.

97
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:01,550
So it's the piglet-fanning game?

98
00:03:01,550 --> 00:03:02,240
I think so.

99
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:05,030
Game rules for this round.

100
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:07,320
Four islanders
stand at the starting line,

101
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,550
hole the palm fan

102
00:03:08,550 --> 00:03:11,190
and fan the piglet into the target basket.

103
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:12,240
That's a success.

104
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:13,880
There are two rounds.

105
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,440
The winner of each round

106
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:15,960
will get

107
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,670
(Date Relay Card)
a Date Relay Card.

108
00:03:17,670 --> 00:03:19,080
Come on, babe.

109
00:03:19,260 --> 00:03:19,670
Let's go.

110
00:03:19,670 --> 00:03:20,390
Let's count.

111
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:22,190
Three,

112
00:03:22,190 --> 00:03:23,470
two, one.

113
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:24,800
Go.

114
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,000
It's not even moving.

115
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,620
(Lazy piglet)

116
00:03:30,100 --> 00:03:30,550
(Ah!)

117
00:03:30,550 --> 00:03:31,390
(Don't cry, piggy)
Sorry.

118
00:03:34,060 --> 00:03:36,100
(Graceful)

119
00:03:36,100 --> 00:03:38,020
(Sending piglet blessings)

120
00:03:38,180 --> 00:03:40,020
(Come on; Nap for 2 sec)

121
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:41,750
(Snuggling)

122
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:42,440
This is chaos.

123
00:03:42,820 --> 00:03:44,220
(Got two piglets)

124
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,160
Chaos.

125
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:45,500
(Messier)

126
00:03:46,390 --> 00:03:47,110
Mine went in.

127
00:03:47,860 --> 00:03:49,420
(Chen Yijia wins)

128
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:50,520
Okay.

129
00:03:51,110 --> 00:03:52,390
Winner of Round 1 is

130
00:03:52,390 --> 00:03:53,440
Chen Yijia.

131
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:57,030
Congrats to Chen Yijia for
winning the Relay date card.

132
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:59,880
Only one Date Relay Card left.

133
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,190
Yijia won the first round.

134
00:04:02,450 --> 00:04:04,720
I'm really worried
she'll pick Zhang Zizheng for the date.

135
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:07,160
So I have to give it my all
in the second round.

136
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:07,960
Come on.

137
00:04:09,030 --> 00:04:10,670
Three, two, one.

138
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:19,500
(Zhu Huiyan is leading for now)

139
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,480
Let's switch positions.

140
00:04:31,790 --> 00:04:33,480
Did my piglet count?

141
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:34,220
(Wu Yihan wins)

142
00:04:34,230 --> 00:04:35,640
Winner of Round 2 is

143
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:36,600
Wu Yihan.

144
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:39,640
Congrats to Wu Yihan
for winning the date card.

145
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,880
So sad.

146
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,760
We finally have a date.

147
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,320
Congrats.

148
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,000
After winning the game,

149
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:48,790
I thought

150
00:04:49,010 --> 00:04:49,790
maybe we'd have to

151
00:04:49,790 --> 00:04:51,110
have dinner together.

152
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,070
I was like, what do I do?

153
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:54,320
Why is it so dramatic?

154
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:57,720
Gomoku skills.

155
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,320
Hello.

156
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:01,550
How's it going?

157
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:02,920
Fanning the piglet into the cage.

158
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,510
Actually pretty fun.

159
00:05:04,510 --> 00:05:05,200
So funny.

160
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,070
Super fun.

161
00:05:07,230 --> 00:05:08,000
Where's your piglet?

162
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:09,040
I didn't take it.

163
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,230
Didn't want to.

164
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,950
Attention, islanders.

165
00:05:13,270 --> 00:05:16,070
Congrats to Chen Yijia and Yang Tianyu.

166
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:17,720
Your date is now active.

167
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:20,660
(Relay)

168
00:05:26,110 --> 00:05:27,790
She actually chose Yang Tianyu.

169
00:05:27,790 --> 00:05:28,720
I don't get it.

170
00:05:29,390 --> 00:05:30,880
I'm curious why she didn't choose me.

171
00:05:31,730 --> 00:05:32,790
You should at least give me

172
00:05:32,790 --> 00:05:33,880
a first chance.

173
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,440
I do like Yijia.

174
00:05:36,230 --> 00:05:38,640
I really had a crush on her
at first sight.

175
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:41,760
But why is her response so...

176
00:05:43,230 --> 00:05:44,230
I can't really explain.

177
00:05:48,340 --> 00:05:49,160
I just feel a bit...

178
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:50,670
Why not

179
00:05:50,670 --> 00:05:51,600
Zhang Zizheng?

180
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:52,510
Then I was

181
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,830
pretty happy.

182
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:57,070
His looks,

183
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:57,920
and his personality.

184
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,040
That's what attracts me.

185
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,390
So I hope this time

186
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:03,110
I can see more of his good points.

187
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,670
Congrats.

188
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:15,230
Congrats to Wu Yihan and Zhang Zizheng.

189
00:06:15,230 --> 00:06:17,230
Your date is now active.

190
00:06:17,230 --> 00:06:20,940
(Relay)

191
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:33,200
What about Tianyu then?

192
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:35,320
Date's over. It's Tianyu's Relay turn.

193
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:36,880
Relay.

194
00:06:38,230 --> 00:06:40,000
That really made him happy.

195
00:06:43,790 --> 00:06:45,200
You finally get a date too.

196
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:45,880
Right?

197
00:06:47,830 --> 00:06:48,600
Let's go.

198
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,920
I finally get to date too.

199
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:52,760
Let's go.

200
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,640
Finally can go out.

201
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:54,790
Can we go out?

202
00:07:00,070 --> 00:07:01,440
Exactly what I thought.

203
00:07:03,100 --> 00:07:03,830
What did you think?

204
00:07:04,110 --> 00:07:04,880
Thinking about them?

205
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:05,320
Yeah.

206
00:07:06,070 --> 00:07:07,160
You're a mind reader.

207
00:07:07,550 --> 00:07:08,790
Exactly what I thought.

208
00:07:09,270 --> 00:07:10,110
Mind reader.

209
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:11,720
You're holding a piglet.

210
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:12,350
What's wrong?

211
00:07:12,350 --> 00:07:13,480
Gonna find Tianyu.

212
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,510
My lucky piglet.

213
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:15,640
Okay.

214
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:18,640
A little heartbroken.

215
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:20,390
You know I like you.

216
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,270
I can't stop you.

217
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,950
You're free to get to know others.

218
00:07:23,230 --> 00:07:24,760
Then I'll do the same.

219
00:07:25,540 --> 00:07:27,020
(Wu Yihan & Zhang Zizheng:
Off to date)

220
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:29,000
Honestly,
I didn't expect you to pick me.

221
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:29,480
To be honest.

222
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:30,950
Why?

223
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,510
Isn't it obvious?

224
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:35,110
Maybe I'm just not

225
00:07:35,110 --> 00:07:36,110
paying attention.

226
00:07:36,130 --> 00:07:36,880
But I never thought

227
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:39,110
I'd get to go out on a date today.

228
00:07:39,110 --> 00:07:40,270
I'm really happy.

229
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,440
Me too.

230
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:42,510
I never thought...

231
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:43,440
I'd end up choosing you.

232
00:07:43,990 --> 00:07:45,110
Yeah, that's the first thing.

233
00:07:45,110 --> 00:07:46,000
Secondly,

234
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,270
there's a date chance.

235
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,270
But honestly, for me,

236
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:52,480
the benefit of winning this afternoon

237
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:54,720
was just being able to go out.

238
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,640
But since you didn't go anyway,

239
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:58,880
so I thought it's fine.

240
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:02,070
Okay, I see.

241
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:07,640
We can still chat on the island,

242
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,920
just the food is worse.

243
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,200
Yeah.

244
00:08:11,230 --> 00:08:12,070
Actually, I haven't

245
00:08:12,070 --> 00:08:14,040
really talked to Yijia all day.

246
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:16,200
Just being petty.

247
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,670
The first date opportunity,

248
00:08:17,670 --> 00:08:18,760
you gave it to Tianyu.

249
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:19,640
I also

250
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:21,640
have someone who's into me too.

251
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:24,320
And I'm okay with her.

252
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:26,160
Then why not choose her?

253
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,070
Are you cold?

254
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:31,070
I'm fine.

255
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:33,200
Maybe cover your legs a bit.

256
00:08:38,230 --> 00:08:38,840
I…

257
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,640
Just guessing

258
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:40,640
why are you sitting here?

259
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:42,000
Is this your good side?

260
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,350
No.

261
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,230
Yeah, my left side looks better.

262
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:47,880
Okay.

263
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:50,520
Am I in a club?

264
00:08:50,740 --> 00:08:52,440
I'll block for you.

265
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:53,840
Okay.

266
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,030
To be honest,

267
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:59,030
when we had that red string thing…

268
00:08:59,030 --> 00:09:00,710
I wanted you to switch places

269
00:09:00,710 --> 00:09:01,640
with that person.

270
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:02,670
You should've said that.

271
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:03,670
You were on the edge.

272
00:09:03,670 --> 00:09:05,280
If you'd said so,
I would've switched.

273
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:06,000
Honestly, I…

274
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,880
But I will…

275
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:07,670
I didn't overthink it.

276
00:09:07,670 --> 00:09:09,030
I thought, if you wanna pull, go for it.

277
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:10,670
Yeah, exactly. Honestly...

278
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:11,350
Then just pull.

279
00:09:11,350 --> 00:09:11,960
Just pull.

280
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,400
Because it was all luck anyway.

281
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,080
You never know.

282
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,280
Kind of a pity though.

283
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:16,790
It's okay though.

284
00:09:17,110 --> 00:09:18,080
Because we're a team.

285
00:09:18,910 --> 00:09:19,840
We could hold hands.

286
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:23,550
Isn't that pretty nice?

287
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:25,280
And to be honest,

288
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:26,440
if I were there,

289
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:28,000
I'd probably be more

290
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,880
bold and charge ahead.

291
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:30,550
